      'slittiYoyo.ops.closing.stats': `<li>Remove crumbs and residue from surfaces and tools</li><li>Store wafers and tools as per procedure (label if using pan storage)</li><li>Quick check: station ‚Äúopening-ready‚Äù</li>`,
      'slittiYoyo.ops.closing.details': `<div class="steps"><strong data-i18n="modal.tab.preparation"></strong><span>1 ¬∑ Clean and dry tools and area.</span><span>2 ¬∑ Store stock with correct labels.</span><span>3 ¬∑ Leave the counter clear and tidy.</span></div>`,

