      'festive.cards.warmServicePandoro.stats': `<li>Crepe plate: clean and dry (never oil)</li><li>Timing: 10 seconds per side</li><li>Immediate service: plate right away to keep volume and warmth</li>`,
      'festive.cards.warmServicePandoro.details': `<div class="steps"><strong data-i18n="modal.tab.preparation"></strong><span>1 ¬∑ Ask for warm/cold preference.</span><span>2 ¬∑ Toast 10" + 10" (no oil).</span><span>3 ¬∑ Plate and suggest a pairing (GELATO/sauce).</span></div><div class="tips"><strong data-i18n="modal.tab.tips"></strong>A warm slice smells amazing and ‚Äúsells‚Äù to nearby guests too.</div>`,

