      'sweetTreats.cards.italianaBeetroot.details': `<div class="steps"><strong data-i18n="modal.tab.preparation"></strong><span>1 ¬∑ Use the beetroot mix (3g powder per 250g mix).</span><span>2 ¬∑ Build it like the classic Italiana.</span><span>3 ¬∑ Colour contrast is the hero: let the filling show.</span></div>`,

